<figureCitation id="137737C5FF90FF85FEABFB0C62F3ABA3" box="[327,411,1163,1187]" captionStart="FIGURES 32 – 38" captionStartId="7.[151,264,1649,1672]" captionTargetBox="[260,1326,707,1623]" captionTargetId="figure@7.[259,1328,702,1626]" captionTargetPageId="7" captionText="FIGURES 32 – 38. Macrostomus nitidus, sp. nov. 32 – 35, paratype male from Goiás, Brazil; 32, left fore leg, posterior view; 33, left mid leg, anterior view; 34, right hind leg, anterior view; 35, wing; 36 – 38, holotype male; 36, tergite 8, dorsal view, right setae omitted; 37, terminalia, lateral view; 38, hypandrium and phallus, lateral view. Scales: 32 – 34 = 0.5 mm; 36 – 38 = 0.2 mm." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/281637/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="46">
